folder: Van Brunt St. & Sackett St., Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Van Brunt St. - Sackett St.
text:
(1)
Van Brunt Street, south of Sackett Street.

March 27, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, showing the S.E. corner upon which once stood the wall paper factories of William H. Mair. In the background, is Union Street. The steeple is that of St. Steven's R.C. Church.

March 27, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.
